page.title: 16BIRDS OF EDALE
page.content: {Resident Birds}Blackbird,Bullfinch, Chaffinch,Carrion Crow,Dipper, Collared Dove,Dunlin,Dunnock,Grouse, Goldfinch,Sparrow Hawk,Heron, Kestrel ,Goldcrest,Greenfinch,Magpie,Mallard, Moorhen,Nuthatch,Tawny Owl,Barn Owl, Little Owl,Partridge,Pheasant,Meadow Pipit,Wood Pigeon,Robin,Rook, House and Tree Sparrow,Starling,Teal, Song and Mistle Thrush,Blue,Great,Coal, Long-tailed Tits,Tree creeper, Woodcock,Great Spotted Woodpecker, Wren. {Summer Visitors.}Chiff chaff,Cuckoo, Curlew,Spotted Flycatcher,Lapwing, Skylark,Linnet,Ring Ouzel,Redstart, Sandpiper,Snipe,Swift,Swallow,House Martin,Pied,Grey and Yellow Wagtails, Whitethroat,Wheatear,Whinchat,Yellow Hammer,Willow and Garden Warblers. {Winter Visitors.}Brambling,Fieldfare Redwing.
